"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-othersport-1928469-Gordon-Ramsay-Adam-Peaty-Olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Gordon Ramsayjoked that Adam Peaty is 'full of s**t' after theTeam GBswimmer dropped a retirement hint during a pre-Olympicschat.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 131, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 26, \"end\": 36, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Adam Peaty\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Peaty, who is dating Ramsay's daughter Holly, is aiming to win his third consecutive gold medal in the men's 100 metre breaststroke.He sat down to chat with the world-famous chef in Paris, with the pair speaking about a variety of topics.\", \"from\": 132, \"to\": 370, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 153, \"end\": 159, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Ramsay\", \"score\": 0.9999978392762083, \"rank\": 2.1273143360191843e-06, \"text\": \"Ramsay\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Ramsay\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Ramsay\"}, {\"begin\": 171, \"end\": 176, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Holly_Flax\", \"score\": 0.9857217286399268, \"rank\": 0.014326565941931272, \"text\": \"Holly\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Holly_Flax\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Holly_Flax\"}, {\"begin\": 314, \"end\": 319, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 6.133627314647963e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ramsay was quick to quiz Peaty on his post-Olympic plans but was unable to get a firm answer with the swimmer keeping his cards close to his chest.\", \"from\": 371, \"to\": 518, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 371, \"end\": 377, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Ramsay\", \"score\": 0.9999978392762083, \"rank\": 2.1273143360191843e-06, \"text\": \"Ramsay\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Ramsay\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Ramsay\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Who knows?\", \"from\": 518, \"to\": 529, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You are smiling, I am not going to give you the pleasure,\\\" said Peaty.\", \"from\": 530, \"to\": 600, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am not going to do it.\", \"from\": 601, \"to\": 626, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You are trapping me.\\\"\", \"from\": 627, \"to\": 648, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ramsay went on to launch a typically foul-mouthed response, firing back: \\\"You are full of s**t!\", \"from\": 649, \"to\": 744, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You are definitely not retiring.\", \"from\": 745, \"to\": 777, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Absolutely, definitely not retiring.\\\"\", \"from\": 778, \"to\": 815, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Pick up your ultimate guide to the Olympics!\", \"from\": 817, \"to\": 861, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Going for Gold provides the day-by-day rundown of what's on and when.\", \"from\": 862, \"to\": 931, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Clickhereto buy.\", \"from\": 932, \"to\": 948, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Discovery+is the new home of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 952, \"to\": 994, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The streamer is set to broadcast 3,800 hours of sport live from Paris.\", \"from\": 995, \"to\": 1065, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1059, \"end\": 1064, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 6.133627314647963e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports fans can getDiscovery+ for \\u00a33.99a month until the end of 2024 via Amazon Prime's video channels.\", \"from\": 1067, \"to\": 1170, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1140, \"end\": 1152, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"score\": 0.7077038071611518, \"rank\": 0.4130205154090584, \"text\": \"Amazon Prime\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This also comes with anAmazon Prime 30-day free trial.\", \"from\": 1171, \"to\": 1225, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The straight-talking chef managed to slip in another cheeky joke before the interview concluded, telling Peaty: \\\"Very best of luck.\", \"from\": 1227, \"to\": 1358, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not f*** this up.\", \"from\": 1359, \"to\": 1379, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It remains to be seen if Peaty will decide to hang up his goggles if he manages to achieve Olympic gold yet again.\", \"from\": 1379, \"to\": 1494, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 29-year-old considered retiring last year and took a break from swimming in order to prioritise his mental health, having been open about his struggles in the past.In an interview withThe Guardianahead of the Olympics, Peaty recalled the moment he began to doubt if he was mentally well enough to compete at the highest level.\", \"from\": 1495, \"to\": 1825, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It started in the water and my goggles filled with tears,\\\" he said.\\\"\", \"from\": 1827, \"to\": 1896, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was crying as I was swimming and I could not acknowledge the situation without crying for months because it had broken me.\", \"from\": 1897, \"to\": 2021, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Remember how Bane breaks Batman's back?\", \"from\": 2022, \"to\": 2061, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2035, \"end\": 2039, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Forgotten_Realms\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.8526433161770544e-14, \"text\": \"Bane\", \"types\": [\"Q1914636\", \"Q11410\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Forgotten_Realms\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Forgotten_Realms\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's what I did to myself mentally.\", \"from\": 2062, \"to\": 2099, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 2101, \"to\": 2210, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 2211, \"to\": 2287, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 2288, \"to\": 2320, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  Do not miss:Olympics star amputates finger just to compete in Paris after horror injury  Do not miss:Athlete 'heartbroken' after being banned from 2024 Olympics for wearing a hijab  Do not miss:Novak Djokovic speaks out on Rafael Nadal as rival suffers 'injury setback'  \\\"I lost all sense of direction and purpose.\", \"from\": 2321, \"to\": 2659, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2407, \"end\": 2412, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 6.133627314647963e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2539, \"end\": 2553, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Novak Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}, {\"begin\": 2568, \"end\": 2580, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rafael Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I thought: 'Why am I even here?'.\", \"from\": 2660, \"to\": 2693, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I said: 'Mel [Marshall, his long-term coach], I have got to get out'.\", \"from\": 2694, \"to\": 2763, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I'd never terminated a training session before.\", \"from\": 2764, \"to\": 2811, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I'd always gone: 'Can I have more, can I have more?'.\", \"from\": 2812, \"to\": 2865, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Like a labrador with a stick.\", \"from\": 2866, \"to\": 2895, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was in the shower, still crying, and Mel said: 'What's up?'.\", \"from\": 2895, \"to\": 2958, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I told her: 'I am done'.\", \"from\": 2959, \"to\": 2983, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Until then I'd ignored everything about that burnout.\", \"from\": 2984, \"to\": 3037, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I did 25m breaststroke and I was like: 'I do not want to do this any more.'\", \"from\": 3038, \"to\": 3113, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I could not think of anything worse and that thought had been brewing for months, potentially years.\", \"from\": 3114, \"to\": 3214, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was no longer worth it.\", \"from\": 3214, \"to\": 3241, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I went to the shop, bought loads of chocolate and ate it.\", \"from\": 3242, \"to\": 3299, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's what you call a breakdown because I lost all discipline, confidence and purpose.\", \"from\": 3300, \"to\": 3385, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \